task_details.name: Module 2: Customer Management API Implementation
task_details.description: Implement complete Customer Management microservice with FastAPI, including customer profiles, KYC, addresses, documents, and notes. Uses same JWT/OAuth authentication as Module 1.

subtasks.name: Module 2: Database Models Implementation
subtasks.description: Create SQLAlchemy models for customers, addresses, KYC, documents, and notes tables

subtasks.name: Module 2: Pydantic Schemas Implementation
subtasks.description: Create Pydantic models for request/response validation including customer profiles, addresses, KYC data

subtasks.name: Module 2: Repository Layer Implementation
subtasks.description: Create repository classes for database operations on customers, addresses, KYC, documents, notes

subtasks.name: Module 2: Service Layer Implementation
subtasks.description: Create service classes for business logic including customer creation, KYC verification, address management

subtasks.name: Module 2: Router/API Endpoints Implementation
subtasks.description: Create FastAPI routers for customer endpoints including CRUD operations, KYC, addresses, documents

subtasks.name: Module 2: Main Application Setup
subtasks.description: Create main.py, __init__.py files and configure FastAPI application for Module 2

subtasks.name: Module 2: Configuration and Dependencies
subtasks.description: Create config.py, requirements.txt, .env.example for Module 2

subtasks.name: Module 2: Docker Configuration
subtasks.description: Create Dockerfile and update docker-compose.yml for Module 2

subtasks.name: Module 2: Testing Implementation
subtasks.description: Create unit and integration tests for Module 2 endpoints and business logic

subtasks.name: Module 2: Documentation
subtasks.description: Create README.md, API documentation, and usage examples for Module 2
